<paragraph blockId="1.[151,924,1697,1722]" box="[151,924,1697,1722]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52">
Our diagnosis of the 
<taxonomicName box="[364,512,1697,1722]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthinae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Melolonthinae</taxonomicName>
below is based largely on 
<bibRefCitation author="Evans, A. V." box="[781,920,1697,1721]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52" pagination="51 - 60" refId="ref13564" refString="Evans, A. V. (2002) Melolonthinae. In: Arnett, R. H., Thomas, M. C., Skelley, P. E. &amp; Frank, J. H. (Eds.), American Beetles. Vol. 2. Polyphaga: Scarabaeoidea through Curculionoidea. CRC Press, Boca Raton, Florida, pp. 51 - 60." type="book chapter" year="2002">Evans (2002)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
